69
00:06:19,294 --> 00:06:22,573
nor gebahaltn hot men zi zuntik, derfar vos

70
00:06:22,573 --> 00:06:27,438
⟨s'i-⟩ biz mir zenen gekumen, i- biz ikh bin gekumen tsu forn tsu der levaye...

71
00:06:28,896 --> 00:06:37,226
⟨un⟩ s'iz geven a shreklekher shney mit a frost, nor m'hot zi getrogn biz in heylikn ort arayn. biz in, grub hot men zi getrogn,

72
00:06:37,553 --> 00:06:45,107
