un zi fleg undz shtendik nor dertseyln vos s'iz geven a mol, ⟨,⟩ funem Bal-Shem,

76
00:06:55,407 --> 00:07:03,028
un far vos me darf moyre hobn, vos me meg un vos me tor nit. zi hot undz gelernt moyde. zi hot undz gelernt shabes oyf der nakht got fun Avrom.

77
00:07:03,372 --> 00:07:06,437
un mir zenen geven shtark fargleybt in ir.

78
00:07:07,472 --> 00:07:08,175
UNK

79
00:07:08,198 --> 00:07:11,651
zi iz geven shtark a reyne, yidene.

80
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:16,224
⟨i⟩n dem, tog vos zi hot gedarft shtarbn hot zi gefilt az zi shtarbt.

81
00:07:16,281 --> 00:07:18,975
dos iz geven erev khanuke.

82
00:07:19,588 --> 00:07:22,167
 hot zi mayn muter avekgeshikt fun der shtub,

83
00:07:22,167 --> 00:07:25,928
un hot gezogt, "gey, vestu koyfn di eyniklekh, mayne ureyniklekh,

84
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,187
PODARKes,

85
00:07:27,187 --> 00:07:29,471
un tsu mir loz araynkumen di shkheyne."

86
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,762
di shkheyne iz nor gekumen, un zi hot ⟨nor⟩ gegibn gelt.

87
00:07:33,308 --> 00:07:39,326
un mayn muter hot gezen az zi shtarbt. zogt zi, "mame, zog mir, ver se kumt dir, bay vemen se kumt dir gelt."

88
00:07:39,332 --> 00:07:41,199
vayl zi fleg tseteyln.

89
00:07:41,661 --> 00:07:45,817
hot zi gezogt, "ver s'vet hobn got in harts vet aleyn opgibn,

90
00:07:45,817 --> 00:07:47,443
un ver se hot nit,

91
00:07:47,584 --> 00:07:49,639
iz loz dos ot ⟨ot⟩ azoy zayn."

92
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:54,547
iz nor eyn shkheyne hot opgegibn etlekhe un fertsik rubl,

93
00:07:55,313 --> 00:07:59,323
hot mayn muter nokh derleygt un hot mir gekoyft a fingerl a PAMYAT',

94
00:07:59,835 --> 00:08:02,141
az ikh zol hobn a ayndenk fun der baben.

95
00:08:03,818 --> 00:08:04,723
o!

96
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:10,556
 zi hot gehat a shtark a shver lebn, vayl zi iz geblibn eyne aleyn

97
00:08:10,556 --> 00:08:14,471
fun zeks un tsvontsik yor, a almone mit,

98
00:08:14,471 --> 00:08:17,565
mayn muter iz nokh geven bay ir in boykh.

99
00:08:17,689 --> 00:08:19,336
der zeyde iz geshtorbn

100
00:08:19,495 --> 00:08:21,328
fun a SIMBIRSKe YAZVe.

101
00:08:21,773 --> 00:08:27,616
hot zi zikh shtark gemutshet. zi fleg bakn broyt un makhn konfetn un, ⟨f-⟩

102
00:08:27,616 --> 00:08:28,786
 shpinen,

103
00:08:28,928 --> 00:08:30,486
un, ⟨f-⟩

104
00:08:30,486 --> 00:08:36,161
⟨, ⟩ POLOTNO makhn. alesding hot zi geton, az zi zol kenen ire kinder helfn.

105
00:08:37,551 --> 00:08:44,649
un hot zikh fardint oyfn lebn. un vos zi fleg helf-, ton, hot, iz ⟨g- got⟩, got mit ir, un ⟨se⟩ fleg ⟨ir z-⟩ geyn mit der hant.

106
00:08:44,706 --> 00:08:49,504
oyb hot zi gebakn broyt oyf farkoyfn, iz ir broyt geven dos shenste; me fleg shteyn in otshered.

107
00:08:49,504 --> 00:08:53,441
oyb zi hot gemakht konfetn, iz ire konfetn zenen geven di shenste;

108
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:57,626
me fleg shteyn in otshered tsun ir. oyb zi fleg bakn PECHEN'E,

109
00:08:57,649 --> 00:08:59,342
iz ir PECHEN'E geven...

110
00:08:59,342 --> 00:09:01,423
