114
00:09:16,735 --> 00:09:18,990
zi hot zikh fotografirt oyfn pasport.

115
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:19,951
zi hot oykhet

116
00:09:20,481 --> 00:09:22,449
lib gehat mitsves tsu ton.

117
00:09:22,776 --> 00:09:25,065
zi iz geven shtark a getraye muter.

118
00:09:29,408 --> 00:09:31,444
az ikh bin avekgeforn fun der heym,

119
00:09:33,829 --> 00:09:36,995
hob ikh zey shtark gefelt oyf di eltere yorn,

120
00:09:37,221 --> 00:09:39,459
vayl ikh fleg zey helfn

121
00:09:40,005 --> 00:09:41,231
mit alemen.

122
00:09:42,621 --> 00:09:44,420
nu, vos ken ikh nokh zogn?

123
00:09:45,051 --> 00:09:47,233
in Bershad hot men zi gekent

124
00:09:47,233 --> 00:09:50,549
far a frume yidene vos zi hot lib gehat mitsves tsu ton,

125
00:09:50,549 --> 00:09:52,369
azoy vi di muter ire.

126
00:09:53,914 --> 00:09:55,298
VSЁ.

127
00:10:02,618 --> 00:10:05,700
dos iz mayn foter, Avreml ⟨Trenker⟩.

128
00:10:05,993 --> 00:10:08,282
im hot gekent di gantse shtetl.

129
00:10:08,389 --> 00:10:10,931
ver s'hot gedarft hobn holts oyfn vinter,

130
00:10:11,308 --> 00:10:13,074
ver s'hot gedarft epes...

131
00:10:15,055 --> 00:10:19,268
er hot a shtark a shver lebn oykhet gehat. er iz geblibn yung a yosem.

132
00:10:19,763 --> 00:10:21,174
er hot gearbet

133
00:10:22,918 --> 00:10:24,346
in a ulinye

134
00:10:24,437 --> 00:10:25,933
bay a balebos.

135
00:10:26,091 --> 00:10:30,793
dernokh hot er gearbet nokh a PRO- PRIKAZCHIK, bizkele m'hot RASKURKAL-, -KULIVet

136
00:10:31,069 --> 00:10:34,640
di, vos zey hobn gehat eygene ulinyes, eygene miln.

137
00:10:35,372 --> 00:10:38,285
dernokh fleg er arbetn oyf alerley arbetn.

138
00:10:41,413 --> 00:10:45,221
di OSNOVNOY arbet iz bay im geven vos er fleg forn in vald arayn

139
00:10:45,261 --> 00:10:47,044
un aroysfirn holts.

140
00:10:48,906 --> 00:10:51,043
un az di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn...

141
00:10:51,454 --> 00:10:55,666
nu, hob ikh gezogt, hot men im farnemen keyn Nikolayever kontslager,

142
00:10:55,993 --> 00:10:58,417
un fun dortn iz er gekumen a kranker.

143
00:10:58,677 --> 00:11:00,805
er hot astme gehat,

144
00:11:01,123 --> 00:11:04,864
nor der guter UKHOD vos er hot gehat bay mayn muter,

145
00:11:05,595 --> 00:11:08,306
hot er gekent lebn biz dray un nayntsik yor.

146
00:11:13,223 --> 00:11:14,246
aha.

147
00:11:15,906 --> 00:11:17,554
in nayntsiktn yor

148
00:11:17,779 --> 00:11:20,422
hot men fotografirt undzer shtetl,

149
00:11:21,103 --> 00:11:23,479
ven di yidn hobn ongehoybn aroystsuforn:

150
00:11:23,479 --> 00:11:25,181
di yidishe shil...

151
00:11:25,181 --> 00:11:28,938
vayl se fleg zayn bay undz nokh a yidishe PEREDACHe, "YAKHAD,"

152
00:11:28,938 --> 00:11:31,880
fun Kiev. fleg men kumen un fotografirn.

153
00:11:32,747 --> 00:11:35,643
mir zenen gekumen atin tsu forn tsu zey.

154
00:11:36,544 --> 00:11:38,563
hot mayn muter zikh farklogt,

155
00:11:38,687 --> 00:11:41,128
az der foter iz geven in shil

156
00:11:41,455 --> 00:11:49,110
un m'hot im fotografirt. "oyf vos t⟨oy⟩g es im?" m'hot shtark moyre gehat, vayl me fleg far azelekhe zakhn nokh, sudyen, arestirn.

157
00:11:50,263 --> 00:11:57,142
"tsu vos ⟨toyg im⟩ oyf di eltere yorn? un me zol kholile no⟨kh⟩ di kinder nit, rufn far derfar." hobn mir zikh oysgelakht fun zey,

158
00:11:57,638 --> 00:11:59,373
un mir hobn gezogt az di shil

159
00:11:59,373 --> 00:12:01,558
iz in FINOTDEL oyfn UCHЁТ;

160
00:12:01,558 --> 00:12:06,103
s'iz do tsvontsik mentshn, vos zey geyen un m'hot zey farregistrirt, me tsolt.

161
00:12:06,413 --> 00:12:08,196
"ir darft nit PEREZHIVAen."

162
00:12:08,370 --> 00:12:09,123
nu,

163
00:12:09,467 --> 00:12:11,362
un azoy iz dos shoyn geven.

164
00:12:11,362 --> 00:12:13,427
mit dem hobn mir ⟨U⟩SPOKOet di mame.

165
00:12:14,547 --> 00:12:17,629
un mir hobn nisht gevust tsulib vos m'hot fotografirt.

166
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:22,719
ven mir hobn avekgeshtelt, krik mit

167
00:12:22,719 --> 00:12:27,990
dray, fir khadoshim hobn mir avekgeshtelt atin, a RUSSKe antene, a rusishe.

168
00:12:28,789 --> 00:12:31,196
un mir hobn oyf der nakht VKLYUCHAet.

169
00:12:31,236 --> 00:12:32,833
mir gibn a kuk,

170
00:12:33,565 --> 00:12:36,916
⟨zogt⟩, vi tsvey meydelekh zenen geshtanen

171
00:12:37,699 --> 00:12:40,983
un m'hot dertseylt far vos me bakt matses,

172
00:12:41,260 --> 00:12:43,886
far vos di yidn praven peysekh azoy.

173
00:12:44,787 --> 00:12:47,093
VSЁ, der tekst hot zikh geendikt,

174
00:12:47,605 --> 00:12:49,766
un dernokh dem hot men gevizn,

175
00:12:49,815 --> 00:12:52,964
⟨⟩, dos kleyne shtetele Bershad.

176
00:12:53,055 --> 00:12:55,648
nu, dos iz geven oyf rusish, altsding.

177
00:12:57,477 --> 00:12:59,411
dos hot mayn man derzen.

178
00:12:59,974 --> 00:13:00,980
zogt er,

179
00:13:01,138 --> 00:13:02,299
"gib a kuk!

180
00:13:02,299 --> 00:13:04,206
Bershad vet men bald vayzn."

181
00:13:04,206 --> 00:13:07,058
er hot bald gezen di yidishe gasn,

182
00:13:07,058 --> 00:13:10,920
azoy vi di yidn pakeven di kestlekh oyf aroystsuforn,

183
00:13:12,428 --> 00:13:19,374
di yidishe shil. zogt er, "ot iz er, Genye, gib a kuk, di yidishe shil!" un azoy hot mayn foter, ibern gantsn ekran,

184
00:13:19,431 --> 00:13:20,736
hot men im gevizn,

185
00:13:20,736 --> 00:13:22,749
azoy vi er geyt aroys fun der shil,

186
00:13:24,527 --> 00:13:26,507
dernokh dem nokh fir yidn.

187
00:13:26,507 --> 00:13:29,348
nor dem oyfdernakht kent ir zikh forshteln.

188
00:13:30,687 --> 00:13:34,255
dos iz geven, in nayntsiktn yor hot men fotografirt,

189
00:13:34,255 --> 00:13:37,076
un Rusland hot gevizn dem film

190
00:13:37,521 --> 00:13:39,124
VOT ersht itstert.

191
00:13:39,529 --> 00:13:41,340
dem film hot men gezen

192
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:43,725
in, IZRAIL' oykhet.

193
00:13:44,811 --> 00:13:50,019
⟨m'hot⟩ mir geklungen un m'hot gebetn, az me vet, ⟨ikh⟩ zol aroysshikn di,

194
00:13:50,211 --> 00:13:51,954
 KASSETe,

195
00:13:51,954 --> 00:13:56,434
az zey zoln kenen nokh a mol un nokh a mol zen, vayl shtark a sakh Bershader

196
00:13:56,434 --> 00:13:58,254
in di gasn un ales.

197
00:13:58,429 --> 00:14:04,073
nu, mir hobn gebetn az oyb me vet zayn, zol men undz demlt onklingen, az mir zoln kenen zikh oykhet

198
00:14:04,073 --> 00:14:04,818
mit dem...

199
00:14:05,061 --> 00:14:06,861
mayn foter hot opgelebt

200
00:14:06,861 --> 00:14:08,345
dray un nayntsik yor.

201
00:14:08,706 --> 00:14:10,556
er iz geshtorbn nokh der muter

202
00:14:11,423 --> 00:14:12,508
in IZRAIL'.

203
00:14:12,508 --> 00:14:17,508
di muter oykhet in IZRAIL', nor di muter iz geven alt nayntsik un der foter dray un nayntsik.

204
00:14:21,582 --> 00:14:23,601
dos iz vayter mayn muter,

205
00:14:23,742 --> 00:14:26,255
lebn undzer shtub, oyf undzer gas,

206
00:14:26,255 --> 00:14:28,578
oyf d- vu mir hobn gevoynt dortn,

207
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:30,603
